# Tech Stack Overview

This project uses a Python backend and a static frontend.

**Backend:**
- Python
- HTTP Server (standard library or lightweight framework)
- SQLite3 database
- `speech_recognition` for voice
- `pynput` (or similar) for keyboard control
- WebSockets for real-time frontend updates

**Frontend:**
- Static HTML/CSS/JS served by the backend
- Alpine.js
- DaisyUI (via CDN)
- No build tools

See the full tech stack details here: [tech-stack.md](mdc:memory-bank/tech-stack.md)

